Code:
```repl
import openpyxl
from pathlib import Path

# Load the input spreadsheet path from the provided variable
input_path = Path(input_spreadsheet)

# Open the workbook (read/write)
wb = openpyxl.load_workbook(input_path)

# Gather basic info about each sheet
sheet_info = {}
for ws in wb.worksheets:
    sheet_info[ws.title] = {
        "max_row": ws.max_row,
        "max_column": ws.max_column,
        "cell_count": ws.max_row * ws.max_column,
    }

# Print a summary (truncated to avoid huge output)
print("Workbook loaded from:", input_path)
print("Sheets found:", list(sheet_info.keys()))
for title, info in sheet_info.items():
    print(f"Sheet '{title}': rows={info['max_row']}, cols={info['max_column']}, cells={info['cell_count']}")
```
